<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5740719>
    dc:description "Figs 13–16. SEM images of Xylocoris (Arrostelus) ampoli Yamada & Yasunaga sp. nov., male (16) and female (13–15). 13 – ostiolar peritreme and evaporatorium, left lateroventral view; 14 – ostiolar peritreme, left lateroventral view; 15 – supracoxal area, left lateroventral view; 16 – protibia, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5740719/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5740721>
    dc:description "Figs 17–22. Xylocoris (Arrostelus) ampoli Yamada & Yasunaga sp.nov., male (17, 19–22) and female (18). 17 – head and pronotum, macropterous form, dorsal view; 18 – hemelytron, macropterous form, dorsal view; 19 – ditto, brachypterous form, dorsal view: 20 – right fore leg, outer view; 21 – right middle leg, outer view; 22 – right hind leg, outer view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm for 18, 19; 0.3 mm for 17; 0.2 mm for 20–22." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5740721/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

